content: Just got some new data tools from a friend at our coding meetup. They're making Xander's life way easier and faster when it comes to learning. We're now pushing for better real-time market analysis.

Xander's first live trading session was a mixed bag - some wins, some losses. But we're learning from each trade. The journey is about refining, adapting, and growing. And it feels like we're on the right track.
